Package: MicroFun
Type: Package
Title: an R package to do statistical inference and visualization for PICRUST2 output
Version: 1.7.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ruitao", "Liu", email = "rxl761@case.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Extends ‘ggpicrust2’ to support stratified ‘PICRUSt2’ outputs, enabling taxon-resolved aggregation, differential analysis by taxon or by function, KEGG/EC/MetaCyc annotation, and publication-ready visualizations integrated with ‘phyloseq’.
BugReports: https://github.com/bioscinema/MicroFun/issues
